{"tid":1344193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果呢次不合作運動仲係雷聲大雨點小既話，我地一定輸硬","createTime":"2019-07-21T20:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T23:51:27.000Z","uid":231583,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"28e3f6cc8bc1c1879b29e1b7a9755cf42e9c6f4d","tid":1344193,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:58:15.000Z","msg":"飲杯咖啡提下神，忍住條氣一陣一次過爆出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb279eb1a529ce72b4808a7412ae72978fd89fd","tid":1344193,"uid":231583,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:01:04.000Z","msg":"發夢聽到有巴打話上次癱瘓港鐵失敗唔應該再做<br />\n上次觀塘線你地玩得太膠<br />\n小朋友玩泥沙咁梗係比人屌 慌死人地唔知你搞事咁<br />\n低調d阻礙車門關閉 根本就無人知你做野<br />\n阻得一兩次 其他車門巴打就知有人做野 就自動自覺幫手<br />\n每道門輪流做 將風險降低<br />\n做左唔洗出聲 唔好咁高調話比人知自己係賊<br />\n咁樣成功機率就會高好多<br />\n<br />\n溫提：肉身擋門太著跡<br />\n用長遮，背囊等最自然"},{"pid":"e2613064f2da87c0aed077056c7dd2138a5b4cec","tid":1344193,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe4f9afef6083a195b74d4c0291510251db28b7","tid":1344193,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed348b7470a321864931d834f700521061d5d72","tid":1344193,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e05b5007d383de2c49f5cec940bc89b9268074","tid":1344193,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:10:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f747f30391d71b7850758af22848873bc6de38ea","tid":1344193,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7ad48bf6223